{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":30,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Sampa","CreatedById":130079,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-11T03:12:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Eso, I heard a lot of people using this force opengl thing to use a lot of mods. How do I do this?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-11T04:56:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s Ask the Moderators, not Ask the Modders. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sampa","CreatedById":130079,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-11T05:06:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIt\u0027s Ask the Moderators, not Ask the Modders. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI was thinking that surely the moderators would know as well...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-11T12:11:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF0000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETHIS WORKS IF YOU USE STEAM\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf you are using Steam, you simply open up the properties, then under the \u0022general properties\u0022 tag, click the button that says \u0022Set launch options...\u0022 A new dialogue window will pop up with the warning that it is to be used by advanced users only. Haha, always get a good laugh out of this one... \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEnter exactly \u0022-force-opengl\u0022 close, then close steam and enter back into it. Start KSP like you normally would.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIt\u0027s Ask the Moderators, not Ask the Modders. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHey, top banana - don\u0027t be upset, I got your um, back...peel...top... Um, no biggie, I answered it if it\u0027s about the Steam version... \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-09-11T21:40:59Z\u0022 title=\u002209/11/2015 09:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 11, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by adsii1970\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EdusacconBR","CreatedById":135047,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-12T01:17:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhy is UmbralRaptor name light green?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-12T01:25:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022EdusacconBR\u0022 data-cite=\u0022EdusacconBR\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWhy is UmbralRaptor name light green?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThat\u0027s because he\u0027s a wiki operator.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EdusacconBR","CreatedById":135047,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-12T01:33:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOh, Cool \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ethanadams","CreatedById":136913,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-13T20:19:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Eis my sig okay?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheMoonRover","CreatedById":136199,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T16:11:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFor some reason my reply to the media group application thing need moderator approval.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDo all posts in the announcements forum require moderator approval? And if so, does that apply anywhere else? And if that isn\u0027t the reason, what is?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T16:16:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAll posts in the Announcements subforum need approval, not 100% sure why. No other subforums are that way.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sampa","CreatedById":130079,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T16:21:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAll posts in the Announcements subforum need approval, not 100% sure why. No other subforums are that way.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMaybe to screen out rude posts?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:21:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhy is HTML on in daily kerbal? I see SQUAD uses HTML to embed the videos. Can I test if it works in the replies section?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:25:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHtml is off everywhere unless you\u0027re admin \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:31:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHtml is off everywhere unless you\u0027re admin \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI see this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/CdjOs7m.png\u0022 alt=\u0022CdjOs7m.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:32:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYes, if you have the permissions, it\u0027s on for you, else no, it\u0027s not \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere\u0027s more than one button for html...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:35:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYes, if you have the permissions, it\u0027s on for you, else no, it\u0027s not \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere\u0027s more than one button for html...\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo even though it says it\u0027s on down there for me, it\u0027s really not? Sorry to be dense.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Supernovy","CreatedById":29617,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:50:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPermissions like that are defined per usergroup and per forum.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIn this case, HTML can be posted in the Daily Kerbal forum, but also HTML cannot be posted by regular forum users.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:53:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Supernovy\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Supernovy\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EPermissions like that are defined per usergroup and per forum.\u003Cp\u003EIn this case, HTML can be posted in the Daily Kerbal forum, but also HTML cannot be posted by regular forum users.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI see, so even if I tried to use HTML, it would not let me.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:55:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESounds like a job for the grand forum test thread!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T20:56:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESounds like a job for the grand forum test thread!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt would be, except in kerbal network I see this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/misc.php?do=bbcode\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EBB code\u003C/a\u003E is \u003Cstrong\u003EOn\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/misc.php?do=showsmilies\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESmilies\u003C/a\u003E are \u003Cstrong\u003EOn\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/misc.php?do=bbcode#imgcode\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022%7Boption%7D\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022%7Boption%7D\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E code is \u003Cstrong\u003EOn\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E code is \u003Cstrong\u003EOn\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHTML code is \u003Cstrong\u003EOff\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"r4pt0r","CreatedById":90471,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T21:13:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI forget to look at the Rep numbers all the time. Does rep given for a deleted post also get taken back?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T21:16:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022r4pt0r\u0022 data-cite=\u0022r4pt0r\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI forget to look at the Rep numbers all the time. Does rep given for a deleted post also get taken back?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENo, rep once given, stays with you even if the post is permanently deleted.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whizzkid","CreatedById":126892,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-16T21:21:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhat happens to a users account if it is banned? Are they not allowed to login or is it just a posting ban?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"goldenpeach","CreatedById":34566,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-17T15:08:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou can\u0027t login for the duration of the ban.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou get a message we can choose when the ban is decided.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheMoonRover","CreatedById":136199,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-18T13:37:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhy is it possible to send yourself a private message? (I just discovered that by accident)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: Now that\u0027s a spectacular 300th post...\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}